	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Floating and dockable windows are sometimes called palettes because one of the first such windows was a color picker. First it was generalized to tool palettes that offer a selection of tools the way a regular palette offers a selection of colors, and then it was generalized beyond that.

		

		</td>
